DESC:The Ruins of Azlant Player's Guide provides players with all the spoiler-free information, inspiration, and new rules they'll need to create characters ready to set sail to explore terra incognita in the Ruins of Azlant Adventure Path. Within, players of this campaign will find everything they need to create backgrounds tied to personalities and events vital to Pathfinder Adventure Path's exploration of the lost continent of Azlant, along with new campaign-specific traits to give brave heroes the edge they'll need to take on the dangers of a remote island and the surrounding seas in the Ruins of Azlant Adventure Path. This player's guide also includes a glimpse of the other colonists who are part of the expedition along with the player characters, as well as various class options and advice for characters ready to dive into adventure.
